<text top="88" left="774" width="56" height="14" font="13"><b>S/PV.5935</b></text>
<text top="108" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="0"> </text>
<text top="1081" left="822" width="10" height="14" font="13"><b>3 </b></text>
<text top="1081" left="90" width="44" height="12" font="14">08-42604 </text>
<text top="1096" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="13"><b> </b></text>
<text top="132" left="126" width="7" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="132" left="162" width="295" height="17" font="3">"The Security Council further calls on the </text>
<text top="150" left="126" width="332" height="17" font="3">United Nations and all parties to facilitate the </text>
<text top="168" left="126" width="329" height="17" font="3">rapid and complete deployment of UNAMID and </text>
<text top="186" left="126" width="336" height="17" font="3">on capable Member States to contribute the </text>
<text top="204" left="126" width="332" height="17" font="3">helicopter and transportation units necessary to </text>
<text top="222" left="126" width="345" height="17" font="3">ensure the successful implementation of </text>
<text top="240" left="126" width="150" height="17" font="3">UNAMID's mandate." </text>
<text top="132" left="468" width="7" height="17" font="3"> </text>
